description: [``botocore``] Increase the maximum length of descriptions for Inputs, Detector Models, and Alarm Models
[``botocore``] This release adds a field exposing model quality to read APIs for models. It also adds a model quality field to the API response when creating an inference scheduler.
[``botocore``] MediaLive now supports the ability to restart pipelines in a running channel.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for sharing Systems Manager parameters with other AWS accounts.
